    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boned is a silly, fast-paced multiplayer party game, inspired by arcade beloved Killer Queen and other multi-player frenzies! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the role of a canine astronaut and launch into space. Drill through planets, slingshot around gravitational fields, and bring your team to victory. Collect toys by drilling into the planet cores, then fire it off to eliminate enemies, or take it back to home base to score for your team. Make sure to keep an eye out for “The Bone”, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/ef8f85706470602629859834bf0f386d.poster.avif?t=1741552265\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/ef8f85706470602629859834bf0f386d.webm?t=1741552265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/ef8f85706470602629859834bf0f386d.mp4?t=1741552265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achieve victory in one of three exciting win conditions:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exhaust all of your opponents’ lives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver 8 toys to your home base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig up “The Bone” and hold onto it in a tug-of-war!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/2554bc317dfde290622493764c68e7c2.poster.avif?t=1741552265\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/2554bc317dfde290622493764c68e7c2.webm?t=1741552265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127600/extras/2554bc317dfde290622493764c68e7c2.mp4?t=1741552265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boned has plenty of awesome features that’ll keep you coming back for more and more:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovingly crafted retro-futuristic style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Different Dogs to choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn titles based on your performance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dedicated bark button.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? <strong>Get Boned today!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Note: A controller is required for local multiplayer.</i></p>",
